kon &lt;unk&gt; ( japanese : &lt;unk&gt; hepburn : &lt;unk&gt; &lt;unk&gt; ) is a 2015 japanese drama film directed by kon ichikawa . it was selected as the japanese entry for the best foreign language film at the 88th academy awards but it was not nominated . the film was selected as the thai entry for the best foreign language film at the 88th academy awards but it was not nominated .